      "span_text": "To ascertain the relationship between sTNFRI, sTNFRII and TNF-a, the molar ratios between the soluble receptors with this cytokine were also calculated, as described by Truyens et al.  : C1 ¥ M2/C2, in which C1 and C2 are the respective concentrations of sTNFR and TNF-a while M1 and M2 are the molecular masses of sTNFR (I and II) and monomeric TNF-a, respectively."
